snippet.title: SpringFling iPhone game trailer
snippet.description: SpringFling is an engaging and addictive vertical platformer for the iPhone set in the beautifully rendered world of SpringTown. With the flick of a finger, jump as high as you can without plummeting to the bottom, then brag to your Twitter and Facebook friends or envious onlookers.
